query:
SELECT 
  e.id,
  e.tipoEvento,
  e.dataEvento,
  e.dataEventoFim,
  e.local,
  t.codigo
FROM eventos e
JOIN turmas t ON e.turmaId = t.id
WHERE t.codigo = '654' AND e.tipoEvento LIKE '%estudio%'
ORDER BY e.dataEvento
